description: Traffic is disrupted in dozens of cities in protests against a court's near-total ban on abortion.
title: Poland abortion ruling: Protesters block roads across country
title_page: Poland abortion ruling: Protesters block roads across country - BBC News
maintext: There are just over 1,000 legal abortions every year in Poland, but women's groups say the number of abortions carried out illegally or abroad could be between 80,000 and 120,000.
